<P><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</STRONG> 7.&nbsp; Traps&nbsp;and lockpicking <FONT color=#0000ff><FONT color=#ff0000>(no change planned at this time)</FONT> - perhaps a revision for the future on this</FONT></P>
