		" 
			>
			<DIV>1) <FONT color=#0000ff></FONT>Add more throwing items for rogues to use. <FONT color=#0000ff>*New*</FONT> <BR><BR>- Lack of itemization is preventing good use of the Deadly Aim discipline we received with OoW. <BR>- Throwing items must be summoned in order to be practical, along the lines of Ton Po's Mystical Pouch from Time. <BR><BR>2) <FONT color=#0000ff></FONT>Enhance the Nerves of Steel AA so that it functions against single target spells as well (as is implied by the current description) or, failing that, refund the AA. <FONT color=#0000ff>*Reworded*</FONT> <BR><BR>- This ability is also bugged. Hide is incorrectly being broken by AE spells that have been resisted and the description is wrong. <BR><BR>3) <FONT color=#0000ff></FONT>Improved critical hit AAs such as Veterans Wrath should apply to backstab. <FONT color=#0000ff>*New*</FONT> <BR><BR>4) Minimum bs damage should scale with weapon / Scale Chaotic Stab with weapon damage. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated</FONT><FONT color=#ff0000>) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning </FONT><BR><BR>5) Slightly increase the availability of tradable and single group weapons that allow more casual, unguilded, and/or non raiding rogues to stay relatively viable. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated) </FONT><BR><BR>6) <FONT color=#0000ff></FONT>Assassin’s Strike is still not effective enough for the endurance cost. The endurance cost should be reduced to make it more in line with similar abilities of other classes. <FONT color=#0000ff>*Reworded*</FONT> <BR><BR>7) Shroud of Stealth should make it so monsters see a rogue much more rarely then it does <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being </FONT><FONT color=#ff0000>evaluated) - Most likely this will be considered as part of the class re-envisioning </FONT><BR><BR>8)&nbsp;Make poisons easier to use and less prohibitive in terms of time investment. Some suggestions of how to achieve this are: <FONT color=#0000ff>*Reworded*</FONT><BR><BR>- Implement some form of endless poison or poison conservation AA. <BR>- Increase the drop rate of poison ingredients or make them purchaseable at a reasonable cost. <BR>- Increase the yield of poisons per combine. <BR>- Dramatically increase the yield of poisons per combine, making the poisons yielded no rent. <BR>- Make old world poisons stackable. <BR><BR>9)&nbsp;Add more +backstab damage items at all levels of play.&nbsp; <FONT color=#0000ff>*New*</FONT><BR><BR>10)<FONT color=#0000ff></FONT> Re-evaluate the focus effects on rogue armour sets from Qvic onwards.&nbsp; <FONT color=#0000ff>*New*</FONT><BR><BR>- The armour sets appear to have been copy/pasted a lot rather than individually tailored for each class. This does not work well for rogues because our desires are so specialised. <BR><BR>BUGS: <BR><BR>- Fix the interaction (bug) between sneak/hide and Bard invis. This bug is not always specific to Bard songs. Some rogues have experienced the breaking of hide when a cast invis spell fades. <BR>- <FONT color=#0000ff>*New*</FONT> Assassins Feint (DoN discipline) does not appear to be functioning correctly.&nbsp;<FONT color=#ff0000>- Dev knows of this and it is slated to be fixed</FONT><BR>- <FONT color=#0000ff>*Sort of new*</FONT> Nerves of Steel (AA) is not functioning correctly (see above) <BR></DIV>
