			>
			<DIV><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt; ?Century Gothic?? FONT-FAMILY:>&nbsp;
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>1) Triple Attack </FONT><FONT size=2><FONT color=#0066ff>*New*<BR></FONT>- Add the ability to triple attack for rogues</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><SPAN><FONT size=2>2) Timer Moves <FONT color=#0066ff>*New*</FONT><BR>- Move Twisted Chance to the Deadeye timer<BR>- Move Assassin's Feint line off the Sneak Attack line timer </FONT></SPAN></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>3) Double/Triple backstab </FONT><FONT size=2><FONT color=#0066ff>*New*<BR></FONT>- Double/Triple backstab should function with Siezed Opportunity<BR>- Double/Triple backstab should be affected by the Sneak Attack line</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2><SPAN></SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>4) Scale Assassinate <FONT color=#0066ff>*New*</FONT><BR>- Assassinate should scale with level so that it still functions on light blue / green mobs when you are level 70.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>5) Illusions <FONT color=#0066ff>*New*<BR></FONT>- Add more illusion masks for rogues at all levels of play<BR>- Add illusion: Shadowman or similar "stealthy" appearance.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>6) Shroud of Stealth <FONT color=#0066ff>*Expanded*<BR></FONT>- Add a second Escape on a separate timer or some kind of shadowstep or some other fix to allow rogues to escape from fast moving see-SoS mobs properly.<BR>- Make it possible to identify mobs which see through SoS without conning them</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>7) Position Dependancy <FONT color=#0066ff>*New*<BR></FONT>- Increase rogues frontal damage to make them a bit less dependant on rear position.<BR>- Out of Range / Cannot See should not blow backstab / sneak attack<BR>- Increase hitbox size of mobs, particularly on raid encounters</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>8) Poisons <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated) -&nbsp;will most likely be considered as part of the class re-envisioning</FONT></FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>Make poisons easier to use and less prohibitive in terms of time investment. Some suggestions of how to achieve this are:<BR>- Implement some form of endless poison or poison conservation AA.<BR>- Increase the drop rate of poison ingredients or make them purchaseable at a reasonable cost.<BR>- Increase the yield of poisons per combine.<BR>- Dramatically increase the yield of poisons per combine, making the poisons yielded no rent.<BR>- Make old world and PoP poisons stackable</FONT></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><SPAN><FONT size=2>9) Add more +backstab damage items at all levels of play. <FONT color=#ff0000>(currently being evaluated)</FONT></FONT></SPAN></DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV align=left><FONT size=2>10) AE Rampage <FONT color=#0066ff>*New*<BR></FONT>- Add an additional defence for rogues to avoid AE rampage</FONT></DIV></SPAN></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
